snippet.title: Star Trek Online: Rise of Discovery Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Journey with Gabriel Lorca and Ellen Landry into the past, and learn their journey to Season One of Star Trek: Discovery. Jason Isaacs and Rekha Sharma join the cast of Star Trek Online to play their iconic roles. Plus, gain new items in the brand new Discovery Legends Reputation, and all of your Tier 6 ships can be flown at any level!
